title: CNN Contributor Says America Needs To “Rethink” Safety?!

author: Matt Walsh
description:
Today on the Matt Walsh Show, while DC fails to get its crime problem under control, the female chief of police publicly acknowledged that she doesn’t even know what the term “chain of command” means. That's no surprise. This woman was hired as their DEI officer, before she was promoted to the head of the whole department. Meanwhile the Attorney General of the city has declared that you can’t solve violent crimes by arresting and prosecuting violent criminals. And a CNN contributor announces that, rather than trying to make DC safe, we should instead “rethink safety.” Also, climate lockdowns have officially begun in Canada. And an American lawmaker is asked an important question: what is an American? Her answer could not possibly have been any worse.
